item.dc:creator: @Pblord7 Pblord7
item.description:
@Pblord7 wrote:

if (spell == 12891) {
			frame174(1111,000,000);
			return false;
		}

Then scroll up and find

if (spell == 12891) {
			return 20000;
		}

and replace with

if (spell == 12891) {
			frame174(1125,000,000);
			return 20000;
		}

If this doesn’t work then I may help you tomorrow.
